{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/git-github-settings","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a6f7374d-3cdf-5be7-8bf0-28dad095d4a8","html":"<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">$HOME/.gitconfig</code></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre class=\"language-ini\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"token selector\">[user]</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">    name</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> ユーザ名</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">    email</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> メールアドレス</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">[color]</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">    ui</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> auto</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">[url \"git@github.com:\"]</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">    insteadof</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> https://github.com/</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">[url \"git@gitlab.com:\"]</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">    insteadof</span> <span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> https://gitlab.com/</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>SSH 接続の設定は <code class=\"language-text\">$HOME/.ssh/config</code> に記述</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre class=\"language-ini\"><code class=\"language-ini\">Host github.com\n    User ユーザ名\n    HostName ssh.github.com\n    IdentityFile ~/.ssh/秘密鍵ファイル名\n    ServerAliveInterval 60</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>認証でエラーが出たら GitHub 用の SSH 秘密鍵を登録</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">eval</span> <span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">`</span>ssh-agent<span class=\"token variable\">`</span></span>   <span class=\"token comment\"># Mac では不要</span>\n$ ssh-add <span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/.ssh/秘密鍵ファイル\n$ ssh-add -l   <span class=\"token comment\"># 登録されている秘密鍵を確認</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">$ git log</code> をデフォルトでツリー表示するためにシェルの設定ファイルに以下を追加</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function-name function\">git</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$@</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"log\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">git</span> log --oneline --graph --decorate\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">command</span> <span class=\"token function\">git</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$@</span>\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/git-github-settings","tagSlugs":["/tag/settings/","/tag/git/","/tag/git-hub/","/tag/git-lab/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-01-25","description":"Git([Hub|Lab]) の設定。","tags":["Settings","Git","GitHub","GitLab"],"title":"Git & GitHub & GitLab 用の設定"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/git-github-settings"}}}